@startuml
' Issue #22
' Related ADRs: ADR-0001, ADR-0012, ADR-0013, ADR-0015, ADR-0016 (proposed)
' Guardrail: planned product context; no component or integration is implemented.

title ERP Docflow - Contexto de produto planejado

left to right direction

actor "Usuário operacional" as Operator
actor "Revisor / aprovador" as Reviewer
actor "Administrador" as Admin
actor "Contador / financeiro" as FinanceUser

rectangle "ERP Docflow\n<<planejado / não implementado>>" as System

cloud "Fontes documentais\nUpload / Drive / OneDrive / E-mail" as Sources
cloud "Providers de processamento\nlocais / self-hosted / cloud" as Providers
cloud "Sistemas financeiros,\ncontábeis e bancários" as ExternalSystems

Operator --> System : envia e acompanha documentos
Reviewer --> System : revisa, corrige, aceita ou rejeita
Admin --> System : governa perfis, acesso e operação
FinanceUser --> System : confirma vínculos e efeitos autorizados

Sources --> System : entradas documentais
System --> Providers : capabilities elegíveis
System --> ExternalSystems : integrações após gates

note bottom of System
  Núcleo: DocumentEnvelope, versões, processamento,
  revisão humana, aceite, vínculos e auditoria.
end note

@enduml

